'''科雷娱乐公司'''（{{lang-en|Klei Entertainment Inc.}}）是一家位于[[加拿大|加拿大]][[不列颠哥伦比亚省|不列颠哥伦比亚省]][[温哥华|温哥华]]的[[游戏开发者|电子游戏开发公司]]，由Jamie Cheng于2005年7月成立。公司最著名的作品是Eets系列、Shank系列、《[[忍者之印|忍者之印]]》、《[[饥荒_(游戏)|饥荒]]》、《隐形公司》和《[[缺氧_(遊戲)|缺氧]]》。2021年1月，科雷娱乐成为中国控股集团[[腾讯|腾讯]]的子公司。

== 历史 ==
杰米·陈（Jamie Cheng）于2005年7月创立了科雷娱乐<ref name=":0" />。在科雷成立之前，Cheng在当时[[THQ遊戲公司|THQ]]旗下的[[遺迹娛樂|遺迹娛樂]]担任人工智能[[游戏程序师|程序师]]<ref name="gamasutra igf">{{Cite web|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=11058|title=Road To The IGF: Klei Entertainment's Eets|last=Wallis|first=Alistair|date=2006-09-29|publisher=[[Gamasutra|Gamasutra]]|access-date=2011-01-21|archive-date=2018-01-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180129195523/https://www.gamasutra.com/php-bin/news_index.php?story=11058|dead-url=no}}</ref>。Cheng出售了他在遺迹娛樂赚取的THQ股票，并从他的兄弟那里得到了1万美元贷款，从而积累了科雷的创始资金<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://thecdm.ca/people/workshop-presenters/jamie-cheng |publisher=Centre for Digital Media |access-date=2017-03-17 |title=Profile: Jamie Cheng |archive-date=2018-02-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180203140933/https://thecdm.ca/people/workshop-presenters/jamie-cheng |dead-url=no }}</ref>。科雷在2009年有11名员工<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/25698/QA_Klei_Founder_Cheng_Discusses_Shank_Animation_Repression.php |publisher=Gamasutra |access-date=2011-01-21 |date=2009-10-22 |title=Q&A: Klei Founder Cheng Discusses Shank, Animation, Repression |first=Chris |last=Remo |archive-date=2018-01-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180129195440/https://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/25698/QA_Klei_Founder_Cheng_Discusses_Shank_Animation_Repression.php |dead-url=no }}</ref>，截至2013年5月已经发展到35名员工<ref name=":0">{{Cite web |url=http://www.polygon.com/features/2013/5/29/4362838/the-birth-and-re-birth-of-klei |publisher=Polygon |access-date=2017-03-15 |date=2013-05-29 |title=The Birth and Re-birth of Klei |first=Chris |last=Plante |archive-date=2018-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180112161746/https://www.polygon.com/features/2013/5/29/4362838/the-birth-and-re-birth-of-klei |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

科雷开发的第一款游戏《Eets》最早于2006年3月27日在[[Microsoft_Windows|Microsoft Windows]]发行<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://store.steampowered.com/app/6100/ |publisher=[[Steam|Steam]] |title=Eets on Steam |dead-url=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110202125736/http://store.steampowered.com/app/6100/ |archive-date=2011-02-02 |access-date=2021-01-30 }}</ref>，然后于2010年12月9日在[[MacOS|Mac OS X]]发行<ref name="mac release">{{Cite web |url=http://www.joystiq.com/2010/12/09/eets-unleashed-on-mac-75-off-via-steam/ |title=Eets unleashed on Mac, 75% off via Steam |first=Randy |last=Nelson |date=2010-12-09 |access-date=2010-12-17 |publisher=Joystiq |archive-date=2015-02-02 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150202120438/http://www.joystiq.com/2010/12/09/eets-unleashed-on-mac-75-off-via-steam/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.krugerheavyindustries.com/ |title=Eets: Hunger it's Emotional |publisher=Kruger Heavy Industries |access-date=2010-12-17 |archive-date=2017-07-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170701223747/http://krugerheavyindustries.com/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在这期间，游戏通过Xbox Live Arcade平台移植到Xbox 360上，并于2007年4月25日以《Eets: Chowdown》为名发行，此版本有120个新关卡和一个叫做Marsho Madness的动作迷你游戏。<ref name="kotaku announce">{{Cite web |url=http://kotaku.com/254551/another-xbla-double-pinball-and-eets |title=Another XBLA Double: Pinball and Eets |date=2007-04-23 |first=Mike |last=Fahey |publisher=[[Kotaku|Kotaku]] |access-date=2010-12-17 |dead-url=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121016060919/http://kotaku.com/254551/another-xbla-double-pinball-and-eets |archive-date=2012-10-16 }}</ref><ref name="xbla">{{Cite web |url=http://marketplace.xbox.com/en-US/Product/Eets-Chowdown/66acd000-77fe-1000-9115-d80258410825 |title=Eets: Chowdown - Xbox.com |publisher=[[Xbox|xbox.com]] |access-date=2010-12-17 |archive-date=2017-09-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170909232943/http://marketplace.xbox.com/en-US/Product/Eets-Chowdown/66acd000-77fe-1000-9115-d80258410825 |dead-url=no }}</ref>

公司协助Slick Entertainment开发了[[Adobe_Flash|Adobe Flash]]游戏《N》的Xbox Live Arcade移植版《N+》<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://kleientertainment.com/n/legend-of-zelda-remade-in-n/ |date=2008-03-20 |title=Legend of Zelda remade in N+ |publisher=Klei Entertainment |access-date=2011-01-21 |dead-url=yes |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20101124221355/http://kleientertainment.com/n/legend-of-zelda-remade-in-n/ |archive-date=2010-11-24 }}</ref>。2008年，科雷开发了一款[[大型多人線上遊戲|大型多人在线游戏]]《Sugar Rush》<ref name="Kotaku">{{cite web |url=http://kotaku.com/5018568/nexons-sugar-rush-arena-in-closed-beta |title=Nexon's Sugar Rush Arena in Closed Beta |access-date=2008-07-18 |last=Greene |first=Maggie |date=2008-06-21 |publisher=Kotaku |archive-date=2018-07-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180724002316/https://kotaku.com/5018568/nexons-sugar-rush-arena-in-closed-beta |dead-url=no }}</ref>。2010年8月底，游戏停止运营<ref>{{cite web|url=http://kleientertainment.com/games/sugar-rush/|title=Sugar Rush Free-to-Play online arena combat game|publisher=Klei Entertainment|access-date=2011-01-21|archive-date=2015-06-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150607195718/http://www.kleientertainment.com/games/sugar-rush/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。公司的第四款原创游戏《Shank》在2009年的[[PAX游戏展|PAX游戏展]]上公布<ref name="Shankhandon-GSpot">{{Cite web |url=http://pax.gamespot.com/story/6216832/shank-hands-on |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090907222543/http://pax.gamespot.com/story/6216832/shank-hands-on |dead-url=yes |archive-date=2009-09-07 |title=Shank Hands-On |last=Tong |first=Sophia |date=2009-09-04 |publisher=[[GameSpot|GameSpot]] |access-date=2009-09-05 }}</ref>，于2010年8月24日在[[PlayStation_3|PlayStation 3]]发行，2010年8月25日在[[Xbox_360|Xbox 360]]发行，2010年10月26日在Microsoft Windows发行<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://shankgame.com/news/klei-signs-with-ea-partners-for-shank/ |title=Klei signs with EA Partners for Shank |date=2010-03-04 |first=Jamie |last=Cheng |publisher=Klei Entertainment |access-date=2010-12-07 |archive-date=2011-08-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110827034051/http://shankgame.com/news/klei-signs-with-ea-partners-for-shank/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

科雷开发的生存冒险游戏《[[饥荒_(游戏)|饥荒]]》于2013年4月23日发行。《饥荒》在[[Steam|Steam]]上以2换1的测试版形式发布，玩家可以用一个游戏的价格购买两份游戏。在正式发行之前，科雷以每份15美元的价格卖出了超过30万份游戏。2016年4月21日，科雷发行了《饥荒》的单机多人版本《饥荒：联机版》，该版本有定期更新和单独的[[可下载内容|可下载内容]]<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.klei.com/games/dont-starve-together|title=Don't Starve Together {{!}} Klei Entertainment|website=www.klei.com|language=en|access-date=2017-07-24|archive-date=2017-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171022135648/https://www.klei.com/games/dont-starve-together|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2013年7月2日，公司宣布下一款作品为回合制间谍游戏《隐形公司》（''Invisible, Inc.''），游戏于2015年5月12日发行<ref>{{cite web|title=Invisible Inc.|url=http://www.invisibleincgame.com/|access-date=2014-07-11|archive-date=2014-07-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140702222845/http://www.invisibleincgame.com/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年，科雷娱乐收购了Slick Entertainment，Slick的创始人Nick Waanders曾和Jamie Cheng在遺迹娛樂共事，后来两家公司得以合并<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/289725/On_its_10th_birthday_Viking_Squad_dev_Slick_joins_forces_with_Klei.php|title=On its 10th birthday, Viking Squad dev Slick joins forces with Klei|last=Wawro|first=Alex|access-date=2017-07-24|language=en|archive-date=2017-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170729211004/http://www.gamasutra.com/view/news/289725/On_its_10th_birthday_Viking_Squad_dev_Slick_joins_forces_with_Klei.php|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2021年1月，科雷宣布公司已经同意[[腾讯|腾讯]]收购其大部分股权，科雷将继续拥有旗下产品的完全控制权，但腾讯的收购将帮助他们进入中国游戏市场<ref>{{cite web | url = https://www.gamespot.com/articles/yet-another-game-dev-acquired-by-tencent-and-this-time-its-dont-starve-maker-klei/1100-6486655/ | title = Yet Another Game Dev Acquired By Tencent, And This Time It's Don't Starve Maker Klei | first = Eddie | last = Makuch | date = 2021-01-22 | access-date = 2021-01-22 | work = [[GameSpot|GameSpot]] | archive-date = 2021-01-29 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210129055431/https://www.gamespot.com/articles/yet-another-game-dev-acquired-by-tencent-and-this-time-its-dont-starve-maker-klei/1100-6486655/ | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

== 文化 ==
联合创始人Jamie Cheng寻求创建一种让员工可以平衡工作与生活的公司文化<ref name=":1">{{Cite web|url=https://www.polygon.com/features/2013/5/29/4362838/the-birth-and-re-birth-of-klei|title=The birth and re-birth of Klei|last=Plante|first=Chris|date=2013-05-29|website=Polygon|access-date=2019-01-15|archive-date=2018-02-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180226100333/https://www.polygon.com/features/2013/5/29/4362838/the-birth-and-re-birth-of-klei|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他建立科雷的理念是：游戏工作室可以用合理的预算在正常的工作时间内以公平的价格制作受欢迎、有趣的游戏，并且仍然可以获得成功<ref name=":1" />。科雷在电子游戏行业获得了良好的声誉，成为一个善待员工并保持工作生活平衡的工作室<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://lovethynerd.com/the-problem-with-crunch/|title=Why We Can't Shake Crunch and How We Can Do Better|date=2018-11-05|website=Love Thy Nerd|language=en-US|access-date=2019-01-15|archive-date=2021-01-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210124192412/https://lovethynerd.com/the-problem-with-crunch/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

